{"tid":1677219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（呢鋪大鑊） 真係得罪左美國","createTime":"2019-10-27T03:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T03:44:50.000Z","uid":25240,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b1998f1093a0b5dbb58fc7557abf8e0d283d9a50","tid":1677219,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"有份在美國參議院聯合提案《香港人權及民主法案》的參議員默克利（Jeff Merkley），再發起一項有關香港的提案，要求美國禁止出口人群管制裝備予涉侵犯和平示威者人權的香港警方，<span style=\"color: red;\">並已獲10多位跨黨派參議員支持。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n默克利表示，自6月以來港人定期舉行遊行示威爭取民主，不過香港警方卻用不斷升級的武力去鎮壓，而包括國際特赦組織等人權組織指警察濫用美製的胡椒噴霧、警棍、橡膠子彈及槍械等驅逐示威者，「要求華府禁止出口人群管制裝備予香港警方」，於是他發起今次跨黨派的草案，以確保美製產品不會在海外淪為侵犯人權的工具。<br />\n<br />\n默克利的提案已獲10多位民主及共和兩黨參議員支持，包括曾親身訪港親歷前線抗爭、目睹警方不人道執法方式的斯科特（Rick Scott）、有份提出修改《美國－香港政策法》草案的馬基（Ed Markey）、在參院聯合提案《香港人權與民主法案》的卡丁(Ben Cardin)、曾去信要求蘋果公司恢復讓抗爭地圖app「HKmap即時地圖」上架的懷登（Ron Wyden）等。<br />\n<br />\n支持提案的議員都痛批香港警方以暴力及不正當手段鎮壓示威，有人更直指是聽令於北京去打壓，嚴重侵犯港人爭取自由的人權，強調美方不會視而不見或容忍。<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議員民主黨籍議員麥高文（Jim McGovern），上月也曾提出名為《保護香港法》（PROTECT Hong Kong Act）的法案，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求美國政府禁止向包括港警在內的紀律部隊出售人群管制裝備，議案在本月中已通過並交由參議院排期審議。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】轟港警侵犯人權及暴力鎮壓 美參議員提案禁輸出防暴裝備<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191027/60199474?utm_campaign=usad_redirect&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=usad_mweb&amp;utm_content=landing_page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60199474%3Futm_campaign%3Dusad_redirect%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dusad_mweb%26utm_content%3Dlanding_page&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOeTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=3e327e6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60199474%3Futm_campaign%3Dusad_redirect%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dusad_mweb%26utm_content%3Dlanding_page&h=bebff940\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191027/60199474?utm_campaign=usad_redirect&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=usad_mweb&amp;utm_content=landing_page</a>"},{"pid":"532d3e17184bac420b5aa69f00d05255dc0c1bdb","tid":1677219,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81f71647f0701f692abacfc380cf06278f10c02","tid":1677219,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"D 軍師去曬邊度？<br />\n<br />\n加泰集會係一場贏左無得分，輸左死全家既賭局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668032</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4db21612497736e4f88d4c07af46300a9c4cb3f1","tid":1677219,"uid":25240,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9V1WaZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9V1WaZm.jpg&h=b5ef4480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n默克利轟港警侵犯示威者人權(互聯網)"},{"pid":"4c48bf79b30ed5356f56131f142256ee0f075127","tid":1677219,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:29:56.000Z","msg":"到時成個驚隊用支那野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567ab86d9f400cced3f898e43e1a5124850575f2","tid":1677219,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1776d502ce68cb823675e031da8a9167e49e1838","tid":1677219,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"狗 : 向支那買囉，仲平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 